mark concept used to run selected test if we have 1000 of test then just search the test which is marked adn run
that perticular test only ignore rest of the test

Syntax

first import the mark from pytest

then just write decorator above of function/test which one we want to run mark will search that test and run
that perticular test only.

@mark.engine mean engine is a key where conteroller will go and run that test below of engine mark

ex
@mark.engine
def test_engine_test():
    return start

in this franework we are used the earbud folder test case run only so we are going to mark that test only

@mark.earbud
def test_earbud():
    return perfect

to run this marker we use

Run Command : - pytest -m erabud

it will run that perticular test